g.text: Add support for Azure Container Apps with datadog-init
Adds agent-in-container support for Azure Container Apps, and extends the agent to more easily add other agent-in-container services.
Right now the agent adds four tags for Container App applications:
- app_name (the name of the app in the GCP UI)
- revision (a custom ID denoting a deployment version)
